; The React submodule is huge (it has its own ~1300-package node_modules), so keep it
; out of dune's source scan. react-client.js in this directory is generated by
; `npm run react-client-generate` and committed; the react-server-dom-esbuild library
; copies it in as a melange runtime dep, so building server-reason-react needs neither
; Node nor the submodule — only regeneration does.

(dirs :standard \ react)
